---
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="badge">v0.3</div>
    <p class="pain">Agent Skills are scattered. Installing them shouldn't be risky.</p>
    <h1>
      One command to <span class="accent">fetch</span>, <span class="accent">scan</span>, and <span class="accent">run</span> any Agent Skill.
    </h1>
    <p class="tagline">
      skillx pulls skills from any Git host or directory, scans them with 23 security rules,
      injects into your agent, and auto-cleans when done.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="/getting-started/" class="cta-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/skillx-run/skillx" class="cta-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
    </div>
    <div class="install-bar">
      <code>curl -fsSL https://skillx.run/install.sh | sh</code>
      <button class="copy-btn" data-text="curl -fsSL https://skillx.run/install.sh | sh" aria-label="Copy">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
          <path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V4a2 2 0 012-2h9a2 2 0 012 2v1"></path>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
    <a href="/getting-started/installation/" class="install-more">More install options &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.hero .copy-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      const text = btn.getAttribute('data-text') || '';
      await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
      btn.classList.add('copied');
      setTimeout(() => btn.classList.remove('copied'), 1500);
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
    color: #a5b4fc;
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pain {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .accent {
    color: #6366f1;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: #6366f1;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: #4f46e5;
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    border-color: #6366f1;
  }

  .install-bar {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: #0f172a;
    border: 1px solid #1e293b;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .install-bar code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #a5b4fc;
  }

  .copy-btn {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: #64748b;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 4px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .copy-btn:hover {
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  .copy-btn.copied {
    color: #22c55e;
  }

  .install-more {
    display: block;
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .install-more:hover {
    color: #a5b4fc;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    }
    .install-bar code {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
